{
  "id": "adv_event_2207_01_04",
  "title": "サイアクの\n環境",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――アイドルミュージックフェス前日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Day before Idol Music Festival",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "向こうに見えるのがスリクスが歌うステージです\n今日はここでリハーサルをして最終調整をします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The stage over there is where IIIX will perform.\nWe'll have rehearsals here today for final adjustments.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.8,
      "endTime": 9.520082262599999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "あそこで歌うの？\nなんか思ってたより小っちゃいんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are we going to sing over there?\nIt's smaller than I expected.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.7333333333,
      "endTime": 14.6149659476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "客席の広さもメインステージとは比べものにならないわ\n五分の一……いえ、それ以下の狭さかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The size of the audience area is incomparable to the main stage.\nIt's about one-fifth… no‚ even smaller than that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.8,
      "endTime": 24.2979589462,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "音響設備もボロくない？　プレタポルテにいた頃は\nもっといい設備のステージを使ってたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The sound equipment sucks. We used stages with\nbetter facilities back in Pret-A-Porter.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.5,
      "endTime": 31.8769615174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "フェスのスタッフもいるんですから\nあまり大きな声で狭いとかボロいとか言わないで下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are festival staff as well.\nPlease don't loudly complain about how small or bad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.0666666667,
      "endTime": 37.9044669787,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "ステージの狭さに合わせてダンスをアレンジして……\n音響はパフォーマンスでカバー出来るから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We'll adjust our dance to fit the small stage…\nWe can cover the sound with our performance…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.1,
      "endTime": 44.968118095499996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "なんかI-UNITYの後にも\nこんなことあったよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ after I-UNITY‚\nthere was something like this too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.3,
      "endTime": 49.2333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "とにかくリハーサルを始めましょう\n明日の本番に向けて完璧に仕上げるわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ let's start the rehearsal.\nLet's perfect it for tomorrow's main event!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.3666666667,
      "endTime": 54.3487338586,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと待って下さい\n三人ともまだステージに上がっちゃダメです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait a moment.\nNone of you should go on the stage yet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.6666666667,
      "endTime": 59.1345728557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "リハーサルをするのはスリクスだけじゃありません\n他のグループもいるのでちゃんと順番を守って下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not just IIIX rehearsing.\nOther groups are also here‚ so please follow the order properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.3333333333,
      "endTime": 65.7227665265,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "えー、めんどくさいなあ\n前の事務所にいた頃は順番なんて気にしなかったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚ it's so annoying.\nWe didn't care about the order before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.9333333333,
      "endTime": 73.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "あの頃は事務所の影響力もあって\nどの現場でも私達は優遇されていたものね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We were favored at any venue due to the agency's influence.\nWe were always given special treatment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.7333333333,
      "endTime": 80.39999999999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "プレタポルテでは特別扱いしていたかもしれませんが\n今のみなさんは星見プロの所属なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You might have received special treatment at Pret-A-Porter.\nBut now‚ you all belong to Hoshimi Pro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.6,
      "endTime": 86.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ここではみなさんを特別扱いしません\nきちんとルールに従って下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We won't give you special treatment here.\nPlease follow the rules properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.9333333333,
      "endTime": 92.0006124815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "え～……\nちょっとくらい融通してくれてもいいじゃん、ケチ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh…\nIt wouldn't hurt to be a bit more flexible‚ stingy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.2,
      "endTime": 98.39999999999999,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7933.333333299998
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ここがみなさんの楽屋になります\n出番が来るまでここで待機していて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This will be your waiting room.\nPlease wait here until your turn comes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.9333333333,
      "endTime": 106.0903856595,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "え？　これが楽屋ですか？\n私達の他にも人が沢山いますけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Is this the waiting room?\nBesides us‚ there are so many other people…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.3,
      "endTime": 112.2381886809,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "楽屋は個室じゃないんですか！？\n今までスリクスの楽屋はずっと個室だったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn't the waiting room supposed to be a private room?!\nIIIX' waiting room has always been a private room until now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.4333333333,
      "endTime": 118.08369611110001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "大人数が参加するフェスでは大部屋が普通なんです\n個室を使えるのは一部のトップアーティストだけです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In festivals with a large number of participants‚ a shared room is common.\nOnly a few top artists get to use private rooms.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.3333333333,
      "endTime": 125.7924291986,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4じゃなくなった私達に\n個室を与える価値はないってこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ for us who are no longer part of the BIG4‚\nthere's no value in giving us a private room?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.0666666667,
      "endTime": 130.76666666659997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "はあ！？　kanaがそのへんのアイドル達と\n一緒の部屋なんて、ありえないんですけど！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hah?! kana sharing a room with those craps\nis a harassment!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.9,
      "endTime": 135.960051873,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "だから、そういうことは大声で言わないで下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please don't say such things loudly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.1666666667,
      "endTime": 139.8737187068,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_04-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "……なんだかこの部屋蒸し暑くないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Isn't this room too stuffy?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.0666666667,
      "endTime": 142.6476870696,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
